could not load plugin @opentelemetry/plugin-http of module http. Error: Cannot find module '@opentelemetry/plugin-http'`\n     - **节点**: `aiops-k8s-05`\n     - **Pod**: `paymentservice-1`\n     - **出现次数**: `1`\n\n2. **frontend**:\n   - **日志2**: \n     - **内容**: `{\"error\":\"failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = failed to charge card: could not charge the card: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.55.4:50051: connect: connection refused\\\"\",\"http.req.id\":\"2fa34118-f8fb-4684-9d4b-9814aecb53cd\",\"http.req.method\":\"POST\",\"http.req.path\":\"/cart/checkout\",\"message\":\"request error\",\"session\":\"5a33103e-42ee-4286-9681-c13e274e252d\",\"severity\":\"error\",\"timestamp\":\"2025-06-14T01:10:31.008056625Z\"}`\n     - **节点**: `aiops-k8s-04`\n     - **Pod**: `frontend-2`\n     - **出现次数**: `1`\n\n3. **paymentservice**:\n   - **日志3**:\n     - **内容**: `PluginLoader#load: could not load plugin @opentelemetry/plugin-grpc-js of module @grpc/grpc-js. Error: Cannot find module '@opentelemetry/plugin-grpc-js'`\n     - **节点**: `aiops-k8s-05`\n     - **Pod**: `paymentservice-1`\n     - **出现次数**: `1`\n\n### 初步分析：\n- **detected_log_keys**:\n  - `paymentservice--plugin`\n  - `frontend--connection refused`\n  - `transport`\n  - `Error while dialing`\n  \n#### Hypotheses:\n1. **frontend**可能存在端口配置问题：\n   - **component**: `paymentservice`（被调用方）\n   - **reason**: `connection refused` 因为无法连接到 `paymentservice`，可能是其端口配置错误导致。\n   - **evidence**: `transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.55.4:50051: connect: connection refused` \n\n2. **paymentservice** 插件加载问题：\n   - **component**: `paymentservice`\n   - **reason**: `Cannot find module` 引起插件加载失败\n   - **evidence**: `PluginLoader#load: could not load plugin @opentelemetry/plugin-http`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"paymentservice--plugin\", \"frontend--connection refused\", \"transport\", \"Error while dialing\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Plugin loading failure: Cannot load module '@opentelemetry/plugin-http'\",\n      \"evidence\": \"PluginLoader#load: could not load plugin @opentelemetry/plugin-http of module http. Error: Cannot find module '@opentelemetry/plugin-http'\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Plugin loading failure: Cannot load module '@opentelemetry/plugin-grpc-js'\",\n      \"evidence\": \"PluginLoader#load: could not load plugin @opentelemetry/plugin-grpc-js of module @grpc/grpc-js. Error: Cannot find module '@opentelemetry/plugin-grpc-js'\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"connection refused when dialing paymentservice\",\n      \"evidence\": \"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.55.4:50051: connect: connection refused\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n这次分析标记为 `NEUTRAL`，现阶段并未对根本原因作出明确结论。需要进一步调查进行排除。", "trace_analysis_findings": "根据异常期间的调用链数据分析，以下是显著异常调用链及潜在的原因分析：\n\n### 异常调用链及表现\n\n1. **Checkout Service to Shipping Service**\n   - **延迟倍数**: 5.82 倍（从正常 12518.42 增加到异常 72866.0）\n   - **异常次数**: 2 次\n   - **异常现象**: 响应延迟大幅增加\n  \n2. **Cart Service调用Redis**\n   - **HGET 操作延迟倍数**: 8.06 倍（从正常 1553.16 增加到异常 12525.91）\n   - **异常次数**: 1 次\n   - **异常现象**: 响应延迟大幅增加\n  \n3. **Checkout Service调用Email Service**\n   - **延迟倍数**: 3.88 倍（从正常 20617.15 增加到异常 80199.0）\n   - **异常次数**: 1 次\n   - **异常现象**: 响应延迟大幅增加\n\n4. **Checkout Service调用Payment Service**\n   - **异常现象**: `connection refused` 错误\n   - **异常次数**: 1 次\n   - **可能原因**: Payment Service 未能响应连接请求\n  \n5. **Frontend调用Checkout Service**\n   - **PlaceOrder操作响应延迟倍数**: 2.00 倍（从正常 144331.8 增加到异常 288889.0）\n   - **异常现象**: 部分请求失败，状态码 500 错误\n    \n### 错误传播路径\n\n- **Checkout Service调用Payment Service遇到“connection refused”**，是系统中连接被拒的关键点。\n- **Frontend在调用Checkout Service时的PlaceOrder操作失败**，已经确认部分失败原因是由于无法连接到Payment Service。\n  \n### 问题原因推测\n- **Network或服务故障**：Checkout Service对Payment Service的连接请求被拒绝，可能是由于Payment Service挂掉或网络连接问题。\n- **资源耗尽或负载过高**：多个服务在异常期间延迟显著增大，可能是资源耗尽导致的性能下降。\n\n### 输出\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\",\n    \"checkoutservice->emailservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"延迟从12518.42增加到72866.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Redis操作延迟从1553.16增加到12525.91\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Email服务调用延迟从20617.15增加到80199.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"connection refused错误\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"PlaceOrder操作延迟从144331.8增加到288889.0\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
